data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the gated community of Doe Valley! This stunning three-bedroom, two-bath residence boasts luxurious living in a serene setting with access to exceptional community amenities such as a sparkling pool and golf course.   Step inside to discover beautiful hard surface flooring that spans the entire home, providing an elegant and cohesive feel.  The open-concept kitchen, living, and dining area features a large kitchen island perfect for entertaining, top-of-the-line appliances, and a spacious walk-in pantry for all your storage needs. Outside, you’ll find a covered back deck perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or hosting gatherings. The privacy fence ensures a secluded and peaceful backyard space while the fire pit adds a cozy touch for relaxing evenings. Don’t miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your new home.
